This guy is a house. I see him fitting perfectly into the gap left by [Bloodbraid Elf](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Bloodbraid Elf) in modern jund. I think I'll call him Mr. Tumnus.  

@Continue The loyalty-abilities-aren't-mana-abilities clause has been in the comp rules for forever. Interesting that they've only now been able to use it. Cards like [Pithing Needle](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Pithing Needle) can choke off the first ability too.  

@Lord\_of\_Tresserhorn This is RG we're talking about. Creatures and lands are all they play; it's basically "Put the top seven cards of your library on the battlefield."
